    </p>

    <p>
        Our mission is to create a digital ecosystem where farmers, renewable energy providers, and environmental enthusiasts come together to:
    </p>

    <ul>
        <li>Promote eco-friendly farming practices</li>
        <li>Enable access to solar, wind, and biogas solutions</li>
        <li>Educate through community forums and digital training</li>
        <li>Empower agricultural businesses to thrive sustainably</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
        Whether you're a small-scale farmer or a green energy innovator, Agri-Energy Connect is your space to learn, grow, and connect.
